Description

WSDL

The service property document. Describes the data model provided by data service.

CSDL

The data model file. Uses the common schema definition language (CSDL). Learn more: [MC–CSDL]: Conceptual Schema Definition File Format (official Microsoft documentation).

EDMX

An *.xml file. Create it using programs for working with the EDM model. The programs are included in the Entity Framework. Learn more: [MC–EDMX]: Entity Data Model for Data Services Packaging Format (official Microsoft documentation).
